<div><head>《始學篇》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.2">天地立，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.3">有天皇十三頭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.4">號曰天靈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.5">治萬八千歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.6">以木德王。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.7">徐堅《初學記》卷九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.8">地皇十一頭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.9">治萬八千歲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-1a.10">《初學記》卷九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.2">人皇九頭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.3">兄弟各三分人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.4">各三百歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.5">依山川土地之勢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.6">財度九州，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.7">各居其一方。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.8">因是而區別。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.10">上古皆穴處，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.11">有聖人教之巢居，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.12">號大巢氏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.13">今南方人巢居，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.14">北方人穴居，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.15">古之遺俗也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-2a.16">《太平御覽》卷七十八、《初學記》卷九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.2">龍淵善相。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.3">篇句佚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.4">據注補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.5">有龍淵者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.6">桓靈時善相人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.7">於聽音聲尤妙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.8">二千石相者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.9">龍淵下床贊之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.10">令長起侍贊之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.11">自六百石以下皆坐而言之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.12">先相張濟當以財得三公，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.13">濟常依淵以觀視，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.14">有相者輒往求之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.15">會解瀆侯往相，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.16">至門問：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.17">「當至貴何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.18">憂貧乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.19">侯去。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.20">淵謂濟曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.21">「可厚事之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.22">濟遂往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.23">盡為償債，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.24">別數百萬修居業。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.25">桓帝崩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.26">無嗣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.27">解瀆侯入為天子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.28">而濟遂至司空。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-3a.29">《太平御覽》卷三百八十八引項氏《始學篇注》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.2">漢侍中蟬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.3">刻蟬像，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.4">常侍但為璫而不蟬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.5">未詳何代所改也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1393_CHANT_001-4a.6">《南齊書‧輿服志》引項氏說。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
